{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-177-integer-angled-quadrilaterals","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 177: Pravougaonik sa četiri strane i uglovima celih brojeva","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka je ABCD četvorougaoniknik sa dijagonalama AC i BD. Na svakom uglu, dijagonala formira ugao sa parom stranica, stvarajući tako osam uglova na ćoškovima.</p>\n<img alt=\"mstatili wa pande nne ABCD, wenye diagonal AC na BD\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/integer-angled-quadrilaterals.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Na primer, u kutu A, dva ugla su CAD, CAB.</p>\n<p>Nazivamo ovakav četvorougaoni poligon čije sve osam uglova imaju celobrojnu vrednost kada se mere u stepenima, „četvorougaono poligon sa celobrojnim uglovima“. Primer četvorugaonika sa celobrojnim uglovima je kvadrat, gde su svi osam ugaona vrhova 45°. Drugi primer je DAC = 20°, BAC = 60°, ABD = 50°, CBD = 30°, BCA = 40°, DCA = 30°, CDB = 80°, ADB = 50°.</p>\n<p>Koja je suma uglova četvorougaonika čiji su uglovi celi brojevi koji nisu jednaki?</p>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> U vašim proračunima možete pretpostaviti da je izmerni ugao celobrojna vrednost ako je unutar tolerancije ${10}^{-9}$ od celobrojne vrednosti.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f41e1000cf542c50ff30","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301812,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-177-integer-angled-quadrilaterals"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function integerAngledQuadrilaterals() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nintegerAngledQuadrilaterals();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>integerAngledQuadrilaterals()</code> should return <code>129325</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(integerAngledQuadrilaterals(), 129325);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-177-integer-angled-quadrilaterals","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-178-step-numbers","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-176-right-angled-triangles-that-share-a-cathetus","id":"5900f41e1000cf542c50ff30","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-177-integer-angled-quadrilaterals"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}